<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>بَابُ التَّثَبُّتِ فِي الْحُكْمِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ اللَّهُ عَزَّ وَجَلَّ:</span> <span class="c3">{يَا أَيُّهَا الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا إِنْ جَاءَكُمْ فَاسِقٌ بِنَبَإٍ فَتَبَيَّنُوا}</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>